{"tid":854621,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【強國Barbie】整容109次靠咩變千萬富婆？ 「女人沒享受過，生出來幹嘛」","createTime":"2018-10-09T13:06:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-09T15:05:15.000Z","uid":25345,"like":4,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"14bd43d0caf64426a5ecc655ee7283d03dfd6956","tid":854621,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T13:06:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181009/large/1539082198_0a99.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181009%2Flarge%2F1539082198_0a99.jpg&h=ee18a576&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181009/large/1539088106_d548.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181009%2Flarge%2F1539088106_d548.jpg&h=0b6683f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n\t\t<br />\n<br />\n「眼睛8次，鼻子9次，胸做了8次......我整容109次，唯獨沒有做過陰道縮緊，現在上手術台都可睡覺。」湖南長沙網紅芙伊伊不斷整容，彷彿成了真人版芭比（Barbie）。日前，《蘋果》記者到長沙見到了她，她直言：「女人沒享受過貴的東西，生出來幹嘛！」<br />\n<br />\n原本出生富裕家庭的她，一度因家道中落，淪落至夜場賣酒，但如今，卻經常能在朋友圈看到她炫耀買名牌，擁有一輛120萬元瑪莎拉蒂（Maserati），還聲稱置有多個物業。想知她如何賺來第一桶金，進而成為千萬富婆"},{"pid":"d41d29f6c11b2f6bdbf7d08621b1598202984b66","tid":854621,"uid":209487,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T13:07:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"589b1571244680ef9ebcaa5740f48449a3308648","tid":854621,"uid":64290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T13:08:24.000Z","msg":"細細個已經練定食青瓜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccc89db69b81140b85b9e76471fd6d8ab7c0e71b","tid":854621,"uid":209487,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T13:08:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"986898da0de2acc8d517dfd20e6e00cfa0ae4fc5","tid":854621,"uid":25468,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T13:08:50.000Z","msg":"對腳一撻撻 , 窮人特徵 <img src=\"/asset